items.title: How To Have Better Meetings!
items.headline: Meeting planning, agenda writing, task accountability, meeting minutes, phrases, virtual meetings, and getting results.
objectives_summary: You will learn to establish a clear reason and outcomes for having a meeing.
You will be challenged to consider if a meeting is truly necessary, who really needs to be there, and what can be accomplished in the time allotted.
The course reviews the basics of agenda development, running a meeting, meeting minutes, and task assignments.
